       "AIMessage(content='LangChain is an open-source framework for building conversational AI models. It provides a set of tools and libraries that enable developers to create, train, and deploy conversational AI models on various platforms.\\n\\nLangChain is designed to be a flexible and modular framework that allows users to build a wide range of conversational AI applications, from simple chatbots to complex language generation systems. The framework is built on top of PyTorch, a popular deep learning library, and provides a range of features such as:\\n\\n1. Model architectures: LangChain provides a set of pre-built model architectures for common NLP tasks, including natural language inference, sentiment analysis, and text classification.\\n2. Data loading: LangChain makes it easy to load and preprocess large datasets for training conversational AI models.\\n3. Training loops: The framework provides a simple way to train models using popular deep learning algorithms such as Adam and SGD.\\n4. Model deployment: LangChain enables users to deploy their trained models on various platforms, including cloud-based services and edge devices.\\n\\nSome of the key features of LangChain include:\\n\\n* Support for multiple NLP tasks and model architectures\\n* Pre-built data loaders for common datasets\\n* Simple and flexible training loops\\n* Easy model deployment on cloud and edge platforms\\n\\nLangChain is particularly well-suited for building conversational AI applications, such as chatbots, voice assistants, and language translation systems. It provides a comprehensive set of tools and libraries that make it easy to build and deploy high-quality conversational AI models.\\n\\nSome examples of use cases for LangChain include:\\n\\n* Building a chatbot that can have conversations with users\\n* Developing a voice assistant that can understand and respond to voice commands\\n* Creating a language translation system that can translate text in real-time\\n\\nOverall, LangChain is a powerful framework for building conversational AI models, providing a wide range of features and tools for developers to create high-quality applications.', additional_kwargs={}, response_metadata={'model': 'llama3.2:latest', 'created_at': '2026-07-15T06:23:50.74453Z', 'done': True, 'done_reason': 'stop', 'total_duration': 16878928208, 'load_duration': 181565125, 'prompt_eval_count': 30, 'prompt_eval_duration': 321570000, 'eval_count': 388, 'eval_duration': 16318112000, 'logprobs': None, 'model_name': 'llama3.2:latest', 'model_provider': 'ollama'}, id='lc_run--019f6471-e5e7-7aa3-afe8-c3e1eedb571c-0', tool_calls=[], invalid_tool_calls=[], usage_metadata={'input_tokens': 30, 'output_tokens': 388, 'total_tokens': 418})"
